<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== VR PHOTO EXHIBITION ==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The '''VR PHOTO EXHIBITION''' is a series of group exhibitions produced by Make Smile Project in collaboration with Fujifilm. The exhibitions display VRChat photographs as physical prints made with Fujifilm's silver halide printing and WALL DECOR products.<ref name="vrpe-vol4">[https://wps-jp.fujifilm.com/202505_vr_photographers/ VR PHOTO EXHIBITION VOL.4〜バーチャルで撮り、リアルで魅せる、新しい写真表現〜] on ''WONDER PHOTO SHOP''. Retrieved March 30, 2026.</ref>
</div>
